&lt;p&gt;You’ll lead, coach, and develop a high-performing retail team while setting the standard for exceptional customer experience, operational excellence, and in-store culture. This includes overseeing staffing, scheduling, training, and performance management, as well as ensuring the store is always customer-ready, well-merchandised, and operating efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Above all, you’ll serve as the face of BRUNT in the community building relationships with local tradespeople, representing our values on the floor, and helping define what “great” looks like for BRUNT retail.&lt;/p&gt;
